
@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam notebackground yellow
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Center {
    +name: String
    +address: String
    +rooms: List<Room>
}

class Room {
    +roomNumber: int
    +maxCapacity: int
    -center: Center
}

class Person {
    +firstName: String
    +lastName: String
    +birthDate: Date
    +sessions: List<Session>
}

class Trainer extends Person {
    +diploma: String
}

class Session {
    +date: Date
    +startTime: Time
    +type: String (optional)
    -room: Room
    -center: Center
    +participants: List<Person>
    +supervisor: Trainer (optional)
}

class Prospect extends Person {
    #hasParticipated: boolean
}

class InternTrainer extends Trainer {
    #hasSupervised: boolean
}

' Association between Center and Room
Center "1" -- "0..*" Room : has

' Association between Room and Session
Room "1" -- "1" Session : contains

' Association between Person and Session
Person "1" -- "1..*" Session : participates in

' Association between Trainer and Session
Trainer "1" -- "0..1" Session : supervises

' Inheritance from Person to Trainer
Person <|-- Trainer

' Inheritance from Person to Prospect
Person <|-- Prospect

' Inheritance from Trainer to InternTrainer
Trainer <|-- InternTrainer

@enduml

---

### Notes:
- The `Person` class is the base class, with inheritance to `Trainer`, `Prospect`, and `InternTrainer`.
- A `Session` can be either individual or group. For group sessions, a `type` is stored.
- A `Session` has a `room` and `center` to determine its location.
- A `Trainer` may supervise one or more group sessions.
- A `Prospect` is a person who hasn't participated in any session yet.
- An `InternTrainer` is a trainer who hasn't supervised any session yet.
- All associations are modeled with appropriate multiplicities.

